ong-term debt, based on quoted market prices for the same or similar debt issues, was", "bbox": [204.2, 1051.9, 1112.5, 1072.7]}, {"text": "approximately $2.8 billion and $3.0 billion at December 31, 2005 and 2004, respectively. Scheduled maturities", "bbox": [162.5, 1076.9, 1112.2, 1097.7]}, {"text": "of long-term debt for the next five years are $67.2 million in 2006, $337.5 million in 2007, $49.1 million in 2008,", "bbox": [162.5, 1101.9, 1112.5, 1122.7]}, {"text": "$8.0 million in 2009 and $33.1 million in 2010.", "bbox": [162.5, 1126.9, 559.5, 1147.7]}, {"text": "During the third quarter of 2005, the Corporation issued $300 million of 4.875% Notes due August 15, 2015.", "bbox": [204.2, 1170.9, 1112.4, 1191.7]}, {"text": "Proceeds from the sale of the notes were used for general corporate purposes and for the reduction of existing", "bbox": [162.5, 1195.9, 1112.5, 1216.7]}, {"text": "indebtedness, including portions of the Corporation’s outstanding commercial paper program.", "bbox": [162.5, 1220.9, 927.9, 1241.7]}, {"text": "At December 31, 2005, the Corporation had fixed-to-floating interest rate swap agreements related to a", "bbox": [204.2, 1264.8, 1112.5, 1285.6]}, {"text": "$500 million 5.0% Note that matures on August 15, 2013.", "bbox": [162.5, 1289.8, 646.9, 1310.6]}, {"text": "At December 31, 2005, the Corporation had $1.5 billion of revolving credit facilities. These facilities,", "bbox": [204.2, 1333.8, 1112.2, 1354.6]}, {"text": "unused at December 31, 2005, permit borrowing at competitive interest rates and are available for general", "bbox": [162.5, 1358.8, 1112.4, 1379.6]}, {"text": "corporate purposes, including backup for commercial paper borrowings. The Corporation pays commitment fees", "bbox": [162.5, 1383.8, 1112.4, 1404.6]}, {"text": "on the unused portion but may cancel the facilities without penalty at any time prior to their expiration. These", "bbox": [162.5, 1408.8, 1112.5, 1429.6]}, {"text": "facilities expire in June 2010.", "bbox": [162.5, 1433.8, 409.0, 1454.6]}, {"text": "51", "bbox": [627.1, 1484.0, 647.9, 1504.8]}]}